Hardware / Emulator Requirements
Requirement	Minimum	Recommended
CPU	Intel 8086/8088	286 or higher
RAM	64 KB	640 KB
Storage	1.44 MB floppy	Any bootable media
Display	VGA compatible	320x200 (Mode 13h)
Input	PS/2 or AT keyboard	Standard 101-key
Sound	PC Speaker Optional

Software (to Build/Run)
Tool	Version	Purpose
NASM	2.15+	Assemble the kernel
QEMU	5.0+	Emulation (recommended)
dd	Any	Create floppy image
Linux/WSL	Any	Build environment
